Package au.csiro.pathling.library.query

Interface QueryDispatcher

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultQueryDispatcher
public interface QueryDispatcher
A a single point for running queries. This exists to decouple the execution of queries from the dispatch, allowing for easier testing and potentially extending the number of types of queries that can be run in the future.
Author:
Piotr Szul, John Grimes
